methods.flush:
Flush any accumulated data in this publisher to the consumer, by invoking its
 accept method.
methods.register:
Register a consumer whose accept method
 will be used when sufficient data is accumulated or on flush().

 
consumer must typically be primed to expect the same chunk types
 that this produces, in the same order.

:param consumer: (io.deephaven.stream.StreamConsumer) - The consumer

text: Chunk-oriented producer for streams of data.
